Armory will display the currently equipped items and allow a user to swap between equipped and unequipped.
If a user tries to equip an item into a slot that is already occupied, swap the two items.
There should also be an option to sell unequipped items back to the game for 50% of their purchase price in gold. No other materials will be refunded. There should be a confirmation window for selling.
There should be a display of values from equipped items.
Equipped items are limited to:
- 1 weapon
- 1 Body armor
- 2 Rings 
- 1 Amulet